4521:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/tasks.c ****          * might bloat the code size, use a lot of stack, and provide different
4522:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/tasks.c ****          * results on different platforms.  An alternative, tiny, third party,
4523:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/tasks.c ****          * and limited functionality implementation of sprintf() is provided in
4524:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/tasks.c ****          * many of the FreeRTOS/Demo sub-directories in a file called
ARM GAS  /tmp/cchbbVys.s 			page 103


4525:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/tasks.c ****          * printf-stdarg.c (note printf-stdarg.c does not provide a full
4526:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/tasks.c ****          * snprintf() implementation!).
4527:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/tasks.c ****          *
4528:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/tasks.c ****          * It is recommended that production systems call uxTaskGetSystemState()
4529:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/tasks.c ****          * directly to get access to raw stats data, rather than indirectly
4530:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/tasks.c ****          * through a call to vTaskList().
4531:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/tasks.c ****          */
4532:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/tasks.c **** 
